Interface SearchResult

  • All Superinterfaces:
    java.io.Serializable
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    SearchResultJSON

    public interface SearchResult
extends java.io.Serializable
    Represents the search results returned from performing a SearchQuery via Twitter.search(SearchQuery)
    Author:
    Aidan Follestad
